    <briefdescription>
<para>Structure to map old mesh BitSets to new. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Structure to easily map topology of <ref refid="group__BooleanGroup_1ga16435c813b6198ecc337b3023c2cc729" kindref="member">MR::boolean</ref> input meshes to result mesh</para>
<para>This structure allows to map faces, vertices and edges of mesh <computeroutput>A</computeroutput> and mesh <computeroutput>B</computeroutput> input of <ref refid="group__BooleanGroup_1ga16435c813b6198ecc337b3023c2cc729" kindref="member">MR::boolean</ref> to result mesh topology primitives <simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="group__BooleanGroup_1ga16435c813b6198ecc337b3023c2cc729" kindref="member">MR::boolean</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
